main event: A UFO sighting occurred in the San Francisco, California area on February 7, 1950.
interesting points: The sighting was observed by both civilian and military sources.
The UFO was described as a conical shape, approximately 30 feet long, and flying at an estimated altitude of 5,000 feet.
The UFO was observed changing position and maneuvering.
The sighting lasted for approximately 10 minutes.
No photographs or physical evidence were collected.
